('95455','32922','5','Country luxury hotel close to Palma de Mallorca for sale'),
('95456','32923','5','This luxury hotel with 89 rooms is situated on a large plot of approximately 200,000m². In a few minutes you can reach two 18 hole golf courses and the sea. It is only a 10-minute drive to the airport. The absolute quiet location (no aircraft noise) and the easy access to Palma, makes this a highly sought-after holiday destination for discerning hotel guests. Apart from its spacious rooms and suites (40m² to 90m²), the hotel offers also a fine spa,indoor pool, a gourmet restaurant, a family pool, anquit adult pool, children''s pool, two tennis courts and over 1000m² meeting rooms.\r\nFor more information, we need a proof of solvency and a signed LOI, witch we will send you gladly\r\n'),
